      </li>
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="45199822">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/62742061/"><img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u62742061-17.jpg" alt="Capt. Backfire" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/45199822/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/45199822/" class="">第112页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/62742061/" class=" " title="Capt. Backfire">Capt. Backfire</a>
                (夏天热。 知了……知了……)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="45199822">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">东汉很多制度承接西汉，并无多少创新之处。农业以及手工业生产技术较前代更加进步。东汉政治豪族土地兼并似乎更加严重。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2017-06-24 16:48</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <p>东汉很多制度承接西汉，并无多少创新之处。农业以及手工业生产技术较前代更加进步。东汉政治豪族土地兼并似乎更加严重。</p>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
